{"tid":370961,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"求救 Router突然用唔到","createTime":"2017-08-23T10:44:18.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-28T14:50:27.000Z","uid":5392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"63192e8f27bb044ee8d6868337c5a6ba339e22df","tid":370961,"uid":5392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T10:44:18.000Z","msg":"今朝11點幾開始就上唔到網，用netvigaxxx<br />\n駁個tplink router 只係for iphone ipad wifi上網用 冇駁電腦個d既<br />\n上網追過好多post都搞唔掂 reset過個router都唔得 pccw又話上網冇問題<br />\n要星期六先搵到人黎check<br />\nreset完個router, setting個到PPPOE已入左上網username同密碼 一路都顯示連線中。。。。拎唔到個ip address<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/23/184218_a228e06461c0e55c080383575bbcb6f5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F23%2F184218_a228e06461c0e55c080383575bbcb6f5.jpg&h=a8a228fb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n￼<br />\n有冇全能既連登巴打可以幫下我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55f1b415c05cc293f397e245a954e1c8ac360982","tid":370961,"uid":54403,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T11:14:29.000Z","msg":"PCCW 係咪有比個盒仔你？<br />\n有既話，斷電，隔5秒，比返電"},{"pid":"2b1c0afbb852de728280f88a71eda5c88bf2f968","tid":370961,"uid":5392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T11:16:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>PCCW 係咪有比個盒仔你？<br />\n有既話，斷電，隔5秒，比返電</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n巴打係咪講個modem? 我冇其他野了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d54c00c12bc8fcdc216130421b0bfe4fae46b60","tid":370961,"uid":5392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T11:23:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>PCCW 係咪有比個盒仔你？<br />\n有既話，斷電，隔5秒，比返電</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n巴打係咪講個modem? 我冇其他野了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n <br />\n其實我抆走哂d線再插過 又熄過哂d野再熄過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n都係唔得"},{"pid":"2bd9e538670a3b3f155873463135e6c7538a8a07","tid":370961,"uid":7043,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T11:28:35.000Z","msg":"叫師傅黎啦仲問"},{"pid":"703594ecda43659302044060b2528a5b0b3f6bf0","tid":370961,"uid":5392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T11:30:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>叫師傅黎啦仲問</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n叫左啦 排到星期六先有師傅黎check<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1208390f82a953075da8fa9ae00635dbb785d06f","tid":370961,"uid":54403,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T11:31:31.000Z","msg":"如果唔經 modem，直插條線落電腦到，<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.digitalcitizen.life/sites/default/files/img/win10_wireless_hidden/hidden_wireless2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.digitalcitizen.life%2Fsites%2Fdefault%2Ffiles%2Fimg%2Fwin10_wireless_hidden%2Fhidden_wireless2.png&h=72d919f8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f71a1b2ed2342583f90f9659bee55eaedd88cf3a","tid":370961,"uid":5392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T11:34:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>如果唔經 modem，直插條線落電腦到，<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.digitalcitizen.life/sites/default/files/img/win10_wireless_hidden/hidden_wireless2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.digitalcitizen.life%2Fsites%2Fdefault%2Ffiles%2Fimg%2Fwin10_wireless_hidden%2Fhidden_wireless2.png&h=72d919f8&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n就係屋企冇電腦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n因為屋企收唔到data <br />\n個寬頻都係用黎放wifi比iphone用<br />\n依家唔知到底係router定寬頻有問題<br />\n<br />\n利申： 電腦白痴絲打 唔識依d野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23318626e6314f7899cede793b2476b656ee02d0","tid":370961,"uid":122939,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T11:39:12.000Z","msg":"setting個頁有無揀自動取得ip <br />\n呀? 你cap個setting頁比人睇下喇"},{"pid":"21f1bf962e71ac2dcc6394930804129018073fdb","tid":370961,"uid":86419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T11:44:52.000Z","msg":"照你咁講你就用緊老電adsl or vdsl<br />\nPPPoE要入返登記人既netvigator既mail<br />\n密碼就登記人身份證頭六個字<br />\n<br />\n如果係光纖就直接用DHCP"},{"pid":"795df2090059d48fc4d36425c51cb7f8aa8c4e57","tid":370961,"uid":5392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T11:46:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>setting個頁有無揀自動取得ip <br />\n呀? 你cap個setting頁比人睇下喇</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/23/194533_d62dc196b5b8ba9c43623c137475aeb9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F23%2F194533_d62dc196b5b8ba9c43623c137475aeb9.jpg&h=ffc16423&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n自動取得ip我都試過都唔得 <br />\n上網搵係netvigaxxx係要入PPPOE"},{"pid":"47a14e839808f08f4756358b690063cdfd0d200d","tid":370961,"uid":122939,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T11:53:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>setting個頁有無揀自動取得ip <br />\n呀? 你cap個setting頁比人睇下喇</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/23/194533_d62dc196b5b8ba9c43623c137475aeb9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F23%2F194533_d62dc196b5b8ba9c43623c137475aeb9.jpg&h=ffc16423&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n自動取得ip我都試過都唔得 <br />\n上網搵係netvigaxxx係要入PPPOE</blockquote><br />\n試吓揀浮動ip."},{"pid":"078a6263b95ac9dd270e23d9b22a0718fb6b57aa","tid":370961,"uid":122939,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T11:56:57.000Z","msg":"第二連線揀浮動ip"},{"pid":"c4c6f3edc24956962b9908ff71950cb748a4d048","tid":370961,"uid":2126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T12:01:10.000Z","msg":"tplink<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fbe45f36f2289b74c1314c1614cd7b5ada5a3023","tid":370961,"uid":46151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T12:02:19.000Z","msg":"tplink<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03c71c23c2dbf1343caac799212dbeb2cdef950a","tid":370961,"uid":5392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T12:04:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>第二連線揀浮動ip</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/23/200329_07bd619caa37d3df9637116ade7ea9b8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F23%2F200329_07bd619caa37d3df9637116ade7ea9b8.jpg&h=2621a6ad&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n試左都係唔得 <br />\n係咪買個新既router就ok? 因為我冇電腦 係咪做唔到setting<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29b9d948ed3d030dd930a47993da4ed5ddd0bc05","tid":370961,"uid":122939,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T12:07:49.000Z","msg":"而家熄咗modem同router,  等五分鐘，先開modem,  等啲燈著好曬，預幾分鐘，之後再開router連線。"},{"pid":"a85b1873168d8ed7b89dc945406565523c98d4aa","tid":370961,"uid":54403,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T12:27:30.000Z","msg":"定其實你將 d 線插錯晒？"},{"pid":"f8e9d3f09fcc0d2c489a93403fa246291cd0cb7b","tid":370961,"uid":5392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T12:31:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>定其實你將 d 線插錯晒？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n冇插錯 都係抆一抆出黎就插番入去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n應該個野壞左呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24ec90784171107135ae1bd2d918b794a9675d32","tid":370961,"uid":54403,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T12:46:52.000Z","msg":"你話個 modem 壞左？"},{"pid":"3682892b6c65a3eb2731d8c17332d8f1c79f714f","tid":370961,"uid":5392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T12:53:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你話個 modem 壞左？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實個modem同router都同平時一樣著個d燈<br />\npccw hotline話睇過冇問題 佢話要師傅check下係咪出面條線有問題 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  冇計<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87cd69e36a9a5d0b686e56cfdf60a01cdebbccb0","tid":370961,"uid":54403,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T12:56:53.000Z","msg":"hotline 話無問題，但又要師傅check下係咪出面條線有問題 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3970a238703385ba41b060b2d920581496098751","tid":370961,"uid":31178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T12:59:23.000Z","msg":"Hotline技術支援應該都係試下remote個modem，之後就話冇事<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94c1da9eb2cc4e0249ee7c9129bad3b690230c70","tid":370961,"uid":281,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T13:02:12.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"873a01778a58fd0bbaeec96dd5cf5ad8718e4124","tid":370961,"uid":5392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T13:10:47.000Z","msg":"有咩router介紹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}